    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏介绍</h2>1. 丰富的游戏剧情<br>当前这个版本提供4个主角供大家选择；不同的主角拥有不同的出生地和主线故事。在主线故事中遇到的小伙伴也会不一样。更有众多的传奇船员在世界各地等待招募<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1856680/extras/d1fd75b2cd2a984eaf30d328474a005c.poster.avif?t=1645262510\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1856680/extras/d1fd75b2cd2a984eaf30d328474a005c.webm?t=1645262510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1856680/extras/d1fd75b2cd2a984eaf30d328474a005c.mp4?t=1645262510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>2. 多样化的航行事件<br>航行过程中不仅要和大自然对抗，还会遇到营养不良、败血症、火灾、鼠患等航行事件，更会和各地的NPC势力产生交集<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1856680/extras/6580bae4852cc1a554a448bac0ca5d12.poster.avif?t=1645262510\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1856680/extras/6580bae4852cc1a554a448bac0ca5d12.webm?t=1645262510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1856680/extras/6580bae4852cc1a554a448bac0ca5d12.mp4?t=1645262510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>3. 开放的航海世界<br>历史遗迹，深海沉船，更有众多的宝物和发现物隐藏在世界各地。扬帆起航，世界等你探索<br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1856680/extras/00fb8d058d6509f8707211a788eef038.poster.avif?t=1645262510\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1856680/extras/00fb8d058d6509f8707211a788eef038.webm?t=1645262510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1856680/extras/00fb8d058d6509f8707211a788eef038.mp4?t=1645262510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>4. 自由的全球贸易<br>游戏提供了160多个港口可供航海家自由贸易。大家可以对港口进行投资，发展港口，港口发展的越好就会带来更多的商品库存，甚至新的商品<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1856680/extras/d7a71c89519dbfe9ae3df22abd502772.poster.avif?t=1645262510\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1856680/extras/d7a71c89519dbfe9ae3df22abd502772.webm?t=1645262510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1856680/extras/d7a71c89519dbfe9ae3df22abd502772.mp4?t=1645262510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>5. 巨舰大炮的浪漫<br>对很多航海家来说，巨舰大炮是浪漫的。我们提供了众多的船型供玩家选择。港口武装度越高，就可以制造更好的巨舰大炮。更有众多的历史名船让航海家获取<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1856680/extras/bb527d804b09cb699669cb9541d63c71.poster.avif?t=1645262510\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1856680/extras/bb527d804b09cb699669cb9541d63c71.webm?t=1645262510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1856680/extras/bb527d804b09cb699669cb9541d63c71.mp4?t=1645262510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>   <br>6. 丰富多彩的成就<br>高达500多种发现物，遍步世界各地。50多艘东西方船只和60多位船员，其中不乏历史名船和传奇船长。在世界各地的酒馆中，还有着独一无二的佳人。征服佳人，不仅可以给航海家带来属性加成，还可以为舰队提供各种增益状态<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1856680/extras/77b3a9dbd83dacea2bceb92550d6d6a0.poster.avif?t=1645262510\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1856680/extras/77b3a9dbd83dacea2bceb92550d6d6a0.webm?t=1645262510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1856680/extras/77b3a9dbd83dacea2bceb92550d6d6a0.mp4?t=1645262510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >开发者的话</h2>非常感谢steam，这是一个能让我们小公司梦想飞翔的平台！我自小就喜欢玩游戏，初中开始玩魂斗罗街机，高中看金庸，大学玩大航海仙剑星际（真是暴露年龄的记忆啊）。。。但是自从大航海系列以后，再也没见过自己喜欢的航海游戏了。现在摸爬滚打混日子升级为制作人了，我就想任性一把，做一款自己喜欢的大航海游戏！老板说不给我收入压力，只要大家喜欢玩（为什么我感觉压力更大了）。我深呼一口气：我们这是一款不用花钱元宝回收一刀999级开局一条狗装备全靠捡的游戏！“啪”一个巴掌，我被打醒了，老板怒吼：那都是骗子！好吧好吧，我们的游戏就一个字“好玩”！两个字“良心制作”。",
